  "text": "Emitted light from the sensor was captured by the same high speed camera on the inverted microscope used for the toxicity experiment. The images were processed with a previously developed in-house program and a lifetime measurement was made [CITATION_1] . The program output a graph of molecular oxygen parts per million versus time. In order to convert the data to fmol/min, the volume of each well had to be determined; because the wet etch manufacturing process resulted in wells with slightly different volumes, each well had to be measured and its volume corroborated with the data from the cell in that well.",
  "correct_citation": {
